title: Exorcist S01E01 HDTV VOSTFR
description: Nothing goes in the Rance family: father began to lose his head, the eldest daughter is cloistered in his room since his university back and even the youngest daughter hears voices in the walls of the house. For the mother, Angela, this is all the work of a demonic force. Convinced that his family is in danger, she appealed to Father Tomas Ortega, who himself will have to cross paths with the mysterious Father Marcus Lang.Adaptation the horror cult film The Exorcist 1973 with Ellen Burstyn and Linda Blair
